SHIN KOKA SAN CEWA DIREBOBIN JIRGIN SAMA SUKAN SHA BARCIN SU A SARARIN SAMANIYA YAYIN DA SUKA DAIDAITA TAFIYAR SU A SAMA? 

Wani bincike da Balpa, kungiyar ma’aikatan jirage ta Biritaniya tayi, ta gano cewa kashi 43% na kwararrun matukan jirgi suna barci a sama bayan sun daidaita komai a sama! 
 
Binciken ya biyo bayan sabbin ka'idojin sufurin jiragen sama sun kara yawan sa'o'in da wadannan kwararrun ke aiki, wanda ba da jimawa ba aka sake yin nazari saboda sakamakon binciken.

Mafiya yawan mutanen da suke cikin jirgin sukan farka Yayinda ake tafiya, kuma sunce in sun Leƙa sukan ga cewa direban yana barci. 
 
Kashi 29 cikin 100 na wadannan matukan jirgi kuma sun yarda cewa suna yin barci, kuma bayan sun farka, sau da yawa sukan sami direban yana barci.
